%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20grown%20up%20in%20Singapore%2C%20I'm%20familiar%20with%20the%20practices%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flao-china-railway-train-ride-countryside-burned-photos-laos-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERamadan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20holy%20month%20for%20Muslims%2C%20where%20they%20fast%20for%20most%20of%20the%20day.%20I%20studied%20Malay%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20in%20school%2C%20I%20often%20fasted%20with%20my%20Muslim%20classmates%20and%20ate%20only%20in%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20in%20many%20cities%20in%20Singapore%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-woman-female-traveler-backpacking-safety-asia-indonesia-jakarta-guide-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndonesia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20non-Muslims%20are%20free%20to%20dine%20in%20public%2C%20so%20long%20as%20they%20do%20so%20respectfully.%20But%20on%20my%20trip%20to%20Brunei%20in%20April%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20burning%20season%20and%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Ramadan%20%E2%80%94%20there%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-support-your-muslim-coworkers-who-are-fasting-during-ramadan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20needed%20to%20observe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20restaurants%20were%20closed%2C%20and%20diners%20weren't%20allowed%20to%20eat%20there%20even%20if%20they%20were%20open%20%E2%80%94%20only%20take-out%20was%20allowed.%20Eating%20in%20public%20was%20a%20major%20faux%20pas%20even%20for%20non-Muslims%2C%20and%20if%20you%20want%20to%20drink%20some%20water%2C%20you%20can%20only%20do%20so%20when%20nobody%20is%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20easy%2C%20especially%20as%20Brunei%20was%20sweltering%20at%20100%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20on%20some%20days.%20I%20made%20do%20by%20returning%20to%20the%20hotel%20for%20lunch%20and%20grabbing%20a%20big%20d