20a%20lack%20of%20evidence%20to%20charge%20Biden%20criminally%2C%20but%20Republicans%20zeroed%20in%20on%20Hur's%20suggestion%20that%20an%20eventual%20post-presidency%20prosecution%20of%20Biden%20could%20render%20him%20a%20sympathetic%20defendant%20because%20of%20his%20age%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftranscript-biden-interview-robert-hur-special-counsel-memory-issues-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseeming%20memory%20problems.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20expectation%20was%20that%20Republicans%20would%20use%20the%20audio%20tapes%20to%20essentially%20show%20Biden%20was%20suffering%20from%20dementia%20or%20senility%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20his%20voice%20or%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20him%20dropping%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20essentially%20be%20raw%20material%20for%20campaign%20ads%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUriarte%20appeared%20to%20make%20a%20similar%20claim%20in%20the%20Monday%20letter%2C%20suggesting%20Republicans%20may%20not%20be%20interested%20in%20actually%20gathering%20evidence%20but%20instead%20requested%20the%20tapes%20%26quot%3Bto%20serve%20political%20purposes%20that%20should%20have%20no%20role%20in%20the%20treatment%20of%20law%20enforcement%20files%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2024%2F04%2F08%2Fbiden-hur-audio-justice-house-subpoena%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20citing%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUriarte%20said%20the%20department%20had%20met%20or%20exceeded%20its%20subpoena%20requests%20for%20the%20case%20and%20accused%20Republicans%20of%20escalating%20the%20matter%20as%20%26quot%3Bconflict%20for%20conflict's%20sake%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F04%2F08%2Fpolitics%2Fdoj-biden-interviews-congress%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22