0rulebook%20for%2011%20months%2C%20writing%20the%20lore%20and%20ironing%20out%20the%20game%20mechanics%20with%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20playtesting.%20Since%20August%2C%20multiple%20game%20masters%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Mercer%2C%20Starke%2C%20and%20Aabria%20Iyengar%20of%20%26quot%3BDimension%2020%26quot%3B%20fame%20%E2%80%94%20have%20run%20their%20iterations%20of%20%26quot%3BCandela%20Obscura%26quot%3B%20and%20helped%20flesh%20out%20the%20game's%20background%20lore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20make%20'Candela%20Obscura'%20accessible%20to%20pick%20up%20for%20people%2C%20from%20experienced%20players%20to%20those%20who%20have%20never%20played%20role-playing%20games%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Starke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wide%20angle%20shot%20of%20the%20basic%20and%20deluxe%20editions%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BCandela%20Obscura%26quot%3B%20core%20rulebook.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660f9f8b16bde8d4ead5f4e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BCandela%20Obscura%26quot%3B%20was%20published%20by%20Critical%20Role's%20publishing%20arm%2C%20Darrington%20Press%2C%20and%20built%20by%20lead%20game%20designers%20Spenser%20Starke%20and%20Rowan%20Hall.%3Cp%3ECritical%20Role%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20%26quot%3BCandela%20Obscura%26quot%3B%20is%20best%20described%20as%20an%20investigative%20paranormal%20horror%20game%20based%20on%20simple%20mechanics.%20People%20who%20want%20to%20play%20the%20game%20don't%20have%20to%20memorize%20%26quot%3B200%20pages%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20designed%20as%20a%20scaffolding%20rather%20than%20an%20entire%20metropolis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20place%20where%20you%20can%20get%20the%20bones%20of%20what%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%20the%