i.insider.com%2F66145b6b1caec1275a6df478%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22727%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20NH%2090%20%26quot%3BCaiman%26quot%3B%20helicopter%20fly%20during%20the%20military%20maneuver%20%26quot%3BOrion%26quot%3B%2C%20over%20the%20camp%20of%20Sissonne%2C%20northeastern%20France%2C%20on%20May%202%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EFRANCOIS%20NASCIMBENI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrance%20also%20did%20not%20say%20what%20type%20of%20helicopter%20engaged%20the%20Houthi%20drone%2C%20but%20both%20of%20the%20French%20warships%20that%20have%20been%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20both%20carry%20NH90%20aircraft%2C%20which%20can%20be%20equipped%20with%20air-to-surface%20missiles%20and%20machine%20guns.%20Because%20the%20drone%20was%20traveling%20in%20the%20air%2C%20the%20crew%20likely%20used%20the%20guns%20to%20take%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20all%20of%20the%20drones%20and%20missiles%20launched%20by%20the%20Houthis%20since%20November%2C%20when%20the%20Iran-backed%20rebels%20began%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-red-sea-aircraft-carrier-houthi-drone-kill-marks-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsistently%20attacking%3C%2Fa%3E%20international%20shipping%20lanes%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Yemen%2C%20have%20been%20shot%20down%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-aircraft-carrier-eisenhower-planes-in-air-constantly-houthis-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Navy%20warships%20or%20fighter%20jets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20coalition%20vessels%20like%20those%20party%20to%20Operation%20Aspides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHelicopter%20engagements%20are%20rarer%20occurrences%2C%20and%20have%20only%20happened%20a%20handful%20of%20times.%20But%20Brynn%20Tannehill%2C%20who%20flew%20the%20SH-60%20Seahawk%2C%20a%20multi-mission%20helicoptered%20used%20by%20the%20Navy%20that's%20based%20on%20the%20UH-60%20Black%20Hawk%2C%20said%20France's%20success%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20particularly%20surprising.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHelicopters%20can%20provide%20a%20relatively%20stable%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20relatively%20maneuverable%2C%26quot%3B%20Tannehill%2C%20now%20a%20US%20Army%20Black%20Hawk%20aviator%20and%20a%20defense%20analyst%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20thing%20against%20them%20is%20that%20they're%20slow%2C%20so%20against%20a%20faster%20target%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20useless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Sept.%2011%2C%202001%20terror%20attacks%2C%20while%20in%20the%20Navy%2C%20Tannehill%20said%20she%20practiced%20simulated%20intercepts%20of%20small%20aircraft%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20would%20move%20at%20a%20speed%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20a%20one-way%20attack%20drone%20%E2%80%94%20and%20boats%20that%20a%20bad%20actor%20could%20theoretically%20pack%20with%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Navy%20Sikorsky%20SH-60%20Seahawk%20with%20the%20Helicopter%20Maritime%20Strike%20Squadron%20Five-One%20(HSM-51)%20flies%20near%20Naval%20Air%20Facility%20in%20Kanagawa.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66145b973f923f7dab05b6e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Navy%20Sikorsky%20SH-60%20Seahawk%20with%20the%20Helicopter%20Maritime%20Strike%20Squadron%20Five-One%20(HSM-51)%20flies%20near%20Naval%20Air%20Facility%20in%20Kanagawa.%3Cp%3EDamon%20Coulter%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20was%20to%20essentially%20figure%20out%20whether%20a%20SH-6o%20could%20maneuver%20into%20position%2C%20put%20a%20gunner%20in%20the%20door%2C%20and%20eliminate%20such%20threats%20with%20a%20.50%20caliber%20machine%20gun%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20simulations%20demonstrated%20that%20helicopters%20were%2C%20indeed%2C%20very%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20they%20found%20was%20that%20helicopters%20are%20pretty%20good%20at%20shooting%20down%20non-maneuvering%2C%20slow%20targets%20out%20the%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20Tannehill%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20because%20you're%20shooting%20sideways%20out%20of%20them%2C%20the%20debris%20doesn't%20even%20come%20back%20at%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20training%20simulations%20have%20ultimately%20been%20brought%20to%20life%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-red-sea-aircraft-carrier-houthi-drone-kill-marks-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eongoing%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20Houthis%20and%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2031%2C%20four%20Houthi%20small%20boats%20attacked%20a%20container%20ship%2C%20prompting%20its%20crew%20to%20issue%20a%20distress%20call.%20Helicopters%20from%20the%20USS%20Dwight%20D.%20Eisenhower%20and%20USS%20Gravely%20%E2%80%94%20an%20American%20aircraft%20carrier%20and%20a%20destroyer%2C%20respectfully%2C%20that%20are%20deployed%20to%20the%20region%20%E2%80%94%20responded%20to%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20responding%20Navy%20helicopters%20arrived%20on%20the%20scene%2C%20the%20Houthis%20opened%20fired%20on%20the%20American%20aircraft%2C%20which%20then%20returned%20fire%20in%20self-defense%2C%20sinking%20three%20of%20the%20four%20Houthi%20small%20boats%20and%20killing%20everyone%20on%20board%2C%20US%20Central%20Command%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCENTCOM%2Fstatus%2F1741381969936834951%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time.%20The%20fourth%20boat%20managed%20to%20flee%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPilots%20are%20'well-trained'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20US%20hasn't%20been%20the%20only%20naval%20force%20to%20destroy%20Houthi%20threats%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20with%20embarked%20helicopters.%20A%20day%20after%20the%20French%20engagement%2C%20on%20March%2021%2C%20a%20helicopter%20at