ing%20up%20for%20shot%20after%20shot%20after%20shot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20limitations%2C%20however%2C%20as%20for%20how%20fast%20the%20helicopter%20can%20travel%2C%20when%20the%20doors%20can%20open%2C%20and%20when%20the%20gunners%20can%20open%20fire.%20The%20pilots%20also%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20they're%20operating%20at%20a%20safe%20distance%20such%20that%20a%20drone%20that%20gets%20hit%20and%20explodes%20doesn't%20send%20shrapnel%20flying%20into%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pilots%20are%20well-trained%2C%26quot%3B%20Tannehill%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20that%20you%20probably%20would've%20practiced%20with%20the%20task%20force%20beforehand%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20when%20it%20does%20happen%2C%20that%20everybody%20knows%20what%20they're%20supposed%20to%20do%20and%20gets%20it%20done%20%E2%80%94%20including%20permission%20to%20fire%20in%20an%20amount%20of%20time%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20do%20it%20before%20the%20target%20presents%20a%20real%20threat%20to%20somebody.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-helicopters-kill-enemy-drones-red-sea-combat-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712611850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6614575516bde8d4ead6bc56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-helicopters-kill-enemy-drones-red-sea-combat-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20US%20naval%20aviator%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20allied%20helicopter%20wins%20against%20drones%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20aren't%20surprising.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-helicopters-kill-enemy-drones-red-sea-combat-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2