e%20planned%20along%20the%20eclipse's%20%26quot%3Bpath%20of%20totality%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20the%20Moon%20could%20be%20seen%20completely%20obscuring%20the%20Sun%20for%20up%20to%20a%20few%20minutes%20--%20weather%20permitting.%20Cloud%20cover%20played%20spoilsport%20over%20parts%20of%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexican%20President%20Andres%20Manuel%20Lopez%20Obrador%20visited%20Sinaloa%20to%20witness%20firsthand%20the%20eclipse%20from%20the%20resort%20of%20Mazatlan%2C%20describing%20the%20event%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20beautiful%2C%20unforgettable%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20gathered%20in%20Mexico%20City%2C%20just%20outside%20the%20path%20of%20totality.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20opportunities%20given%20by%20Earth%20and%20nature%20that%20we%20must%20seize%2C%26quot%3B%2029-year-old%20artist%20Mariana%20Juarez%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20path%20of%20totality%20is%20115%20miles%20(185%20kilometers)%20wide%20and%20home%20to%20nearly%2032%20million%20Americans%2C%20with%20an%20additional%20150%20million%20living%20less%20than%20200%20miles%20from%20the%20strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20that%20can%20be%20seen%20from%20a%20large%20part%20of%20North%20America%20won't%20come%20around%20until%202044.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Freaking%20nuts'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusinesses%20capitalized%20on%20the%20excitement%20with%20special%20events%2C%20while%20hotels%20and%20short-term%20rentals%20in%20prime%20viewing%20locations%20were%20booked%20solid%20for%20months%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Stonehenge%20II%20park%20in%20Ingram%2C%20Texas%20--%20a%20replica%20of%20the%20prehistoric%20arrangement%20of%20stones%20in%20England%20--%20eclipse%20watchers%20gathered%20from%20across%20the%20world%2C%20screaming%20and%20cheering%20at%20the%20moment%20of%20totality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeni%20Lyn%20Hunter%2C%2057%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20Charles%20Guillory%2C%2060%2C%20had%20traveled%20from%20Floresville%2C%20Texas.%20The%20couple%20identified%20as%20%26quot%3Bpagans%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20and%20wore%20Merlin%20hats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20means%20a%20lot%20to%20me%20because%20I%20have%20stage%20four%20cancer%20but%20I'm%20not%20giving%20up%2C%20this%20is%20a%20rebirth%20of%20the%20Sun%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Hunter%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20Russellville%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20more%20than%20300%20couples%20were%20reportedly%20set%20to%20exchange%20vows%20at%20%26quot%3BA%20Total%20Eclipse%20of%20the%20Heart%26quot%3B%20mass%20wedding%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelta%20airlines%20has%20planned%20two%20special%20flights%20along%20the%20path%2C%20while%20many%20schools%20in%20the%20zone%20shut%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Scientific%20windfall%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20science.%20NASA%20planned%20to%20launch%20a%20trio%20of%20sounding%20rockets%20before%2C%20during%20and%20just%20after%20the%20eclipse%20to%20measure%20changes%20caused%20by%20the%20sudden%20darkness%20to%20the%20ionosphere%2C%20an%20upper%20layer%20of%20the%20atmosphere%20important%20for%20long-distance%20radio%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eclipse%20also%20offered%20a%20golden%20opportunity%20to%20study%20the%20Sun's%20corona%2C%20the%20outer%20layer%20of%20its%20atmosphere%20which%20is%20normally%20hidden%20by%20the%20blinding%20light%20of%20the%20surface%2C%20but%20has%20an%20outsized%20impact%20on%20everything%20from%20satellites%20to%20power%20grids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20few%20high%20clouds%20but%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20corona%20is%20clearly%20visible%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20NASA%20heliophysicist%20Michael%20Kirk%20as%20the%20eclipse%20passed%20through%20Dallas.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20that%20spiky%20structure%20just%20poking%20out%20--%20It%20is%20heart-stopping%20beautiful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20thrilled%20that%20the%20Sun%20was%20near%20the%20peak%20of%20its%2011-year%20cycle%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20asymmetrical%20corona.%20As%20the%20eclipse%20unfolded%2C%20the%20rugged%20lunar%20topography%20revealed%20itself%20in%20a%20stunning%20'diamond%20ring'%20effect%2C%20while%20planets%20like%20Venus%20and%20Jupiter%20briefly%20appeared%20in%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStartling%20animal%20behavior%20has%20been%20noted%20during%20past%20eclipses%20--%20roosters%20can%20crow%20as%20the%20darkness%20ends%20believing%20it%20is%20dawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20humans%2C%20eclipses%20trigger%20feelings%20of%20awe%20as%20we%20confront%20our%20place%20within%20the%20vast%20cosmic%20order.%20Individuals%20exhibit%20more%20%26quot%3Bprosocial%26quot%3B%20feelings%20towards%20each%20other%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20shared%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Safety%20first%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20president%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20notoriously%20gazed%20directly%20at%20the%20Sun%20during%20the%202017%20eclipse%2C%20attempted%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20phenomenon%20by%20releasing%20a%20new%20campaign%20ad%20featuring%20his%20larger-than-life%20head%20blocking%20out%20our%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20professionals%20have%20stressed%20not%20to%20follow%20his%20example%2C%20urging%20people%20to%20use%20certified%20eclipse%20glasses%20to%20prevent%20permanent%20retinal%20injury.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20made%20fun%20of%20Trump%20with%20a%20social%20media%20post%20saying%20%26quot%3BDon't%20be%20silly%2C%20folks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20those%20within%20the%20path%20of%20totality%20can%20safely%20remove%20eye%20protection%20and%20admire%20the%20corona%20peeking%20out%20from%20behind%20the%20silhouette%20of%20the%20Moon%20for%20a%20few%20precious%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C