outh.%20However%2C%20what%20caught%20everyone's%20attention%20was%20the%20holstered%20gun%20he%20tried%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20while%20getting%20into%20the%20open-roof%20vehicle%20next%20to%20Siddaramaiah%20campaigning%20for%20Sowmya%20Reddy%20near%20Madiwala%20in%20the%20city's%20south-east.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20showed%20the%20man%20garlanding%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20on%20the%20truck%20with%20a%20firearm%20dangling%20from%20his%20belt.%20As%20he%20climbed%20down%20from%20the%20vehicle%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20the%20others%20noticed%20the%20weapon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20raised%20eyebrows%20and%20several%20questions%20on%20security%20protocol%20violations%20since%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20is%20already%20in%20place.%20Once%20the%20code%20is%20imposed%2C%20all%20firearms%20are%20required%20to%20be%20surrendered%20to%20the%20respective%20police%20station%20and%20any%20exemptions%20can%20only%20be%20obtained%20with%20an%20exempt%20permit.%20The%20arms%20are%20returned%20to%20the%20rightful%20owners%20once%20the%20election%20is%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20one%20Riyaz%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20He%20has%20been%20carrying%20a%20gun%20since%20a%20life-threatening%20assault%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20was%20hence%20exempted%20from%20surrendering%20his%20gun%2C%20he%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20incident%20happened%20close%20to%20Wilson%20Garden.%20Regarding%20the%20weapon%2C%20it%20is%20a%20licensed%20one%20that%20he%20had%20in%20self-defence%20as%20he%20had%20been%20attacked%20before.%20Based%20on%20all%20this%2C%20an%20inquiry%20is%20on%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Bengaluru%20South)%2C%20Lokesh%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETweeting%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20Vijayendra%20Yediyurappa%20-%20the%20son%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20BS%20Yediyurappa%20-%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20election%20co