0Abdullah%20scoffed%20at%20the%20DPAP%20chief's%20remark.%20Mr%20Azad%20has%20%26quot%3Bgot%20instructions%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%20%26quot%3BHis%20party%20announced%20and%20it%20is%20quite%20ingenious%20on%20trying%20to%20back%20out%20and%20say%20he%20hasn't%20made%20up%20his%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20take%20a%20call%20on%20having%20an%20alliance%20for%20assembly%20elections%20after%20parliament%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azad%2C%20also%20a%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20had%20held%20a%20series%20of%20public%20meetings%20earlier%20to%20gauge%20voters'%20reactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLots%20of%20people%20are%20asking%20me%20to%20contest.%20Demand%20of%20my%20being%20in%20parliament%20is%20there...%20but%20there%20are%20voices%20who%20want%20me%20contest%20Assembly%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20--%20stripped%20of%20its%20special%20status%20under%20the%20Constitution's%20Article%20370%20in%20August%202019%20and%20carved%20into%20two%20union%20territories%20--%20has%20not%20had%20an%20assembly%20election%20for%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20hearing%20a%20clutch%20of%20petitions%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20said%20an%20assembly%20election%20had%20to%20be%20held%20by%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712600640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F2hoo62b4_ghulam-nabi-azad-ani_625x300_24_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-ghulam-nabi-azad-says-might-not-contest-j-k-polls-5401851%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%2C%20who%20formed%20his%20own%20party%20after%20quitting%20the%20Congress%2C%20may%20not%20contest%20the%20coming%20general%20election%2C%20even%2