O'Brien.%20Among%20the%20protesting%20MPs%20were%20Dola%20Sen%2C%20Sagarika%20Ghosh%2C%20Saket%20Gokhale%20and%20Shantanu%20Sen.%20Demanding%20a%20%26quot%3Blevel%20playing%20field%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20MPs%20had%20promised%20a%2024-hour%20sit-in%20outside%20the%20Commission's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20action%20started%20an%20hour%20into%20the%20dharna%2C%20when%20the%20leaders%20declined%20repeated%20requests%20to%20leave%20after%20meeting%20the%20poll%20commissioners.%20Visuals%20from%20the%20spot%20showed%20the%2063-year-old%20Mr%20O'Brien%20being%20hauled%20to%20the%20bus%20by%20a%20couple%20of%20policemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20Mr%20O'Brien%2C%20speaking%20to%20reporters%20from%20the%20police%20station%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%2024-hour%20dharna%20will%20continue.%20My%20colleague%20Mohd%20Nadimul%20Haque%20is%20a%20diabetic%20patient.%20Dola%20Sen%20had%20hurt%20her%20leg%20and%20now%20the%20injury%20has%20gotten%20worse.%20But%20we%20are%20here%20to%20fight%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20are%20alleging%20that%20the%20central%20agencies%20are%20focussing%20on%20Opposition%20leaders%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election%20and%20the%20motive%20of%20the%20arrests%20made%20by%20the%20agencies%20is%20purely%20political.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20case%20filed%20in%202022%2C%20an%20arrest%20is%20made%20in%202024%20by%20the%20NIA.%20Law%20and%20order%20is%20a%20state%20subject%20and%20the%20local%20police%20should%20have%20been%20informed%E2%80%A6%20Strictly%20the%20chiefs%20of%20the%20four%20central%20agencies%20should%20be%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Trinamool%20MP%20Dola%20Sen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20manner%20in%20which%20officials%20CBI%2C%20NIA%2C%20ED%20and%20Income%20Tax%20are%20acting%2C%20they%20appear%20to%20be%20branch%20members%20of%20BJP.%20It%20is%20making%20the%20life%20of%20opposition%20difficult.%20A%20member%20of%20BJP%20had%20a%20meeting%20with%20an%20NIA%20official%20at%20the%20latter's%20residence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sagarika%20Ghosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20examples%2C%20she%20said%20in%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20April%205%20and%206%2C%20raids%20were%20conducted%20without%20informing%20local%20police.%20%26quot%3BThis%20time%2C%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20by%20the%20NIA%20in%20a%20two-year-old%20case%E2%80%A6%20Homes%20of%20women%20were%20raided%20at%203%20am%20in%20the%20morning.%20Officials%20barged%20into%20the%20houses%20at%203%20am%2C%20where%20they%20harassed%20and%20molested%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MPs%2C%20she%20said%2C%20have%20requested%20the%20poll%20commission%20to%20change%20the%20chiefs%20of%20NIA%2C%20ED%2C%20CBI%20and%20income%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20comes%20days%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20warning%20that%20at%20a%20recent%20election%20rally%20in%20Jalpaiguri%20that%20action%20against%20corruption%20will%20pick%20up%20pace%20after%20June%204%2C%20when%20the%20results%20of%20the%20election%20are%20to%20be%20declared.%20%26quot%3BShould%20we%20not%20end%20corruption%3F%20Should%20we%20not%20send%20corrupt%20people%20to%20jail%3F%20Should%20we%20not%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20TMC%20corruption%3F%20This%20is%20a%20Modi's%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20chief%20and%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20today%20that%20her%20party%20is%20not%20scared%2C%20even%20though%20the%20BJP%20is%20using%20the%20agencies%20for%20political%20purpose.%20%26quot%3BThey%20say%20Modi%20ka%20Guarantee.%20What%20is%20Modi's%20guarantee%3F%20That%20he%20will%20put%20everyone%20in%20jail%20after%20June%204%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20senior%20Trinamool%20leader%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20met%20Bengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20delegation%20went%20to%20meet%20the%20Election%20Commission%20today.%20The%20way%20women%20MPs%20were%20dragged%20and%20detained%20is%20murder%20of%20the%20republic%20and%20the%20main%20reason%20behind%20this%20murder%20is%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20does%20the%20Election%20Commission%20not%20remove%20the%20NIA%20Director%20and%20NIA%20SP%20despite%20having%20all%20the%20evidence%3F%20If%20West%20Bengal%20DG%20can%20be%20changed%20only%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20then%20why%20are%20the%20NIA%20Director%20and%20NIA%20SP%20not%20removed%20when%20we%20are%20bringing%20out%20the%20facts%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712600520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4r4ceh7s_trinamool-protest-ec-office_625x300_08_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F10-trinamool-mps-sit-on-24-hour-dharna-outside-election-commission-office-5399388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2010-member%20delegation%20of%20Bengal's%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20sitting%20on%20a%20dharna%20outside%20the%20Delhi%20headquarters%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20police%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F10-trinamool-mps-sit-on-24-hour-dharna-outside-election-commission-office-5399388%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F10-trinamool-mps-sit-on-24-hour-dharna-outside-election-commission-office-5399388%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F10-trinamool-mps-sit-on-24-hour-dharna-outside-election-commission-office-5399388%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20market%20capitalisation%20tops%20Rs%20400%20trillion%20as%20indices%20hit%20new%20high%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712600245000%2C%22visua