sinesses%20were%20using%20water%2C%20what%20their%20daily%20consumption%20levels%20were%2C%20and%20started%20thinking%20of%20customised%20solutions%20required%20for%20each%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashidhara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Save%20water%20in%20Bengaluru%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346781%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashidhara%20Kumaraswamy%20%26amp%3B%20Karunaprasada%20Kanavi%2C%20co-founders%20of%20EverythingEco.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Shashidhara%20and%20his%20co-founder%20did%20a%20detailed%20audit%20on%20water%20consumption%20levels%20across%20multiple%20locations%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20they%20found%20that%20each%20business%20or%20residential%20unit%20has%20specific%20requirements%20based%20on%20its%20usage%20pattern.%20In%20certain%20locations%2C%20they%20found%20the%20flow%20rate%20measured%20in%20hand%20washing%20taps%20to%20be%20around%2015%20to%2016%20litres%20per%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTypically%2C%20we%20have%20observed%20that%20when%20you%20buy%20taps%20of%20standard%20fittings%2C%20their%20flow%20rate%20is%20between%2014%20to%2018%20litres%20per%20minute%20based%20on%20water%20pressure.%20Most%20fixtures%20sold%20commercially%20do%20not%20have%20any%20aerators.%20They%20come%20with%20filters%20to%20filter%20out%20the%20dust.%20These%20filters%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20the%20job%20of%20water%20conservation%2C%20but%20only%20ensure%20the%20laminar%20flow%20of%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDuring%20this%20audit%2C%20they%20concluded%20that%20taps%20for%20hand%20washing%20should%20never%20have%20a%20flow%20rate%20of%20more%20than%203%20litres%20per%20minute.%20Similarly%2C%20for%20kitchens%2C%20they%20understood%20that%20people%20required%20a%20higher%20flow%20rate%20but%20not%20more%20than%206%20to%208%20litres%20per%20minute.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20ideal%20scenario%2C%20no%20tap%20should%20have%20a%20flow%20rate%20of%20more%20than%206%20litres%20a%20minute%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shashidhara.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20look%20at%20multiple%20use%20cases%20in%20terms%20of%20hospitals%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20bulk%20washing%20areas%2C%20their%20requirements%20are%20very%20different%20and%20not%20everyone%20can%20live%20with%20spray%20taps%20releasing%203%20litres%20a%20minute.%20We%20started%20looking%20at%20custom%20designs%20and%20solutions.%20Our%20company%20does%20comprehensive%20water%20audits%20for%20businesses%20and%20provides%20solutions%20for%20varied%20sizes%20of%20taps%2C%20addressing%20diverse%20types%20of%20flow%20rates%20that%20are%20required%2C%20and%20implementing%20them%20end-to-end%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAerators%20manufactured%20by%20EverythingECO%20start%20with%20flow%20rates%20(per%20minute)%20of%201%20litre%2C%203%20litres%2C%204%20litres%2C%20and%206%20litres.%20%E2%80%9CAerators%20with%20a%20flow%20rate%20of%200.5%20and%201%20litre%20per%20minute%20usually%20offer%20a%20mist-type%20flow.%20But%20for%20commercial%20and%20residential%20apartments%2C%20this%20flow%20rate%20is%20too%20low%20to%20wash%20hands.%20For%20hand%20wash%20taps%2C%20our%20aerator%20which%20restricts%20flow%20rates%20to%203%20litres%20a%20minute%20is%20popular%20across%20all%20sectors.%20Many%20people%20opt%20for%203%20litres%20a%20minute%20aerator%20for%20their%20kitchen%20taps%20as%20well%2C%20because%20it%20effectively%20covers%20a%20larger%20area%20for%20washing%20utensils.%20If%20customers%20want%20laminar%20flow%20in%20their%20kitchen%20taps%2C%20then%20they%20go%20for%204%20or%206%20litres%20a%20minute%20aerators%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shashidhara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRestrictors%20reduce%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20that%20is%20coming%20out%20from%20the%20pipes%20or%20the%20entry%20points.%20You%20can%20attach%20these%20restrictors%20to%20older%20type%20taps%2C%20health%20faucets%20and%20shower%20heads%20and%20reduce%20the%20flow%20rate%20to%20anywhere%20between%206%20to%209%20litres%20a%20minute.%20Depending%20on%20the%20water%20pressure%20of%20their%20shower%20heads%2C%20people%20can%20use%20restrictors%20to%20limit%20the%20flow%20rate%20to%206%20to%209%20litres%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F_I--BQBbe1Y%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcont