sted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EModi-Shah's%20political%20and%20ideological%20ancestors%20supported%20the%20British%20and%20Muslim%20League%20against%20the%20Indians%20in%20the%20Freedom%20Struggle.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnEven%20today%2C%20they%20are%20invoking%20the%20Muslim%20League%20against%20the%20'Congress%20Nyay%20Patra'%20guided%20and%20shaped%20according%20to%20the%20aspirations%2C%20needs%20and%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1777235124968444093%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi-Shah's%20ideological%20ancestors%20opposed%20Gandhi's%20call%20for%20Quit%20India%20in%201942%2C%20which%20was%20chaired%20by%20Maulana%20Azad.%20There%20is%20a%20stink%20of%20RSS%20in%20Modi%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E's%20speeches...%20BJP's%20electoral%20graph%20is%20plunging%20day%20by%20day.%20Therefore%20RSS%20has%20started%20remembering%20its%20best%20friend%20-%20the%20Muslim%20League!%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20too%2C%20after%20the%20PM's%20initial%20jibe%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20know%20his%20history%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20pointed%20out%20that%20Jana%20Sangh%20founder%20and%20BJP%20ideologue%20Syama%20Prasad%20Mookerjee%20himself%20was%20part%20of%20a%20coalition%20government%20in%20Bengal%20with%20the%20Muslim%20League%20in%20the%20early%201940s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20does%20not%20know%20his%20history.%20It%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20none%20other%20than%20Mookerjee%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20then%2C%20who%20was%20himself%20part%20of%20the%20coalition%20government%20in%20Bengal%20with%20the%20Muslim%20League...%20It%20is%20the%20BJP%2C%20not%20the%20Congress%2C%20that%20believes%20in%20and%20practices%20the%20politics%20of%20divisiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20section%20of%20the%20manifesto%20-%20released%20Friday%20-%20that%20has%20sparked%20this%20row%20is%20a%20guarantee%20to%20increase%20reservation%20for%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20including%20Dalits%2C%20past%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%2050%20per%20cent%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Muslim%20League%20talked%20about%20reservation%20on%20basis%20of%20religion%20in%201929...%20Congress%20is%20repeating%20the%20same%20thing.%20The%20way%20there%20is%20talk%20of%20reservation%20on%20basis%20of%20religion%20and%20promise%20of%20reservation%20beyond%2050%20per%20cent...%20who%20is%20to%20be%20benefitted%2C%20Congress%20should%20make%20it%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-2024-manifesto-focuses-on-unemployment-promises-caste-census-5378978%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECongress%20Manifesto%20Focuses%20On%20Unemployment%2C%20Promises%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20manifesto%20also%20focuses%20on%20job%20creation%20and%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20and%20makes%20several%20other%20promises%2C%20including%20guaranteeing%20MSP%2C%20or%20minimum%20support%20price%2C%20to%20protesting%20farmers%20and%20direct%20cash%20transfers%20to%20women%20heads%20of%20below%20poverty%20line%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%