Fentry%2Fteamsters-boycott-molson-coors-final-four_n_660f19d4e4b09f580bc73689%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2224000%20Farmers%20Are%20Fighting%20Climate%20Crisis%20By%20Growing%20Their%20Own%20Seeds%2C%20Thanks%20to%20One%20Man%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20Eastern%20Himalayas%20where%20the%20Brahmaputra%20river%20meandered%20through%20the%20verdant%20valleys%20of%20Assam%2C%20Neelam%20Dutta%20embarked%20on%20an%20extraordinary%20quest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20was%20not%20your%20ordinary%20villager%3B%20he%20possessed%20a%20deep%20reverence%20for%20the%20land%20and%20its%20treasures.%20With%20each%20passing%20day%2C%20he%20witnessed%20the%20subtle%20yet%20undeniable%20shifts%20in%20the%20climate%2C%20sensing%20the%20looming%20threat%20it%20posed%20to%20the%20cherished%20crops%20of%20his%20ancestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20safeguard%20their%20legacy%2C%20he%20meticulously%20tended%20to%20a%20collection%20of%20seeds%2C%20each%20a%20precious%20heirloom%20from%20generations%20past.%20These%20seeds%2C%20once%20abundant%2C%20were%20now%20disappearing%20%E2%80%94%20victims%20of%20modernisation%20and%20the%20relentless%20march%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Neelam%20refused%20to%20let%20them%20fade%20into%20obscurity.%20He%20understood%20that%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20changing%20climate%2C%20adaptation%20was%20key%2C%20and%20these%20heirlooms%20held%20the%20secrets%20to%20survival.%20His%20endeavour%20became%20a%20symbol%20of%20resilience%2C%20a%20guardian%20of%20tradition%20in%20a%20rapidly%20evolving%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHeirloom%20seeds%2C%20passed%20down%20for%20at%20least%2050%20years%2C%20are%20resistant%20to%20floods.%20This%20is%20a%20vital%20trait%20in%20combating%20food%20security%20threats%20posed%20by%20climate%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20Neelam%2C%20now%2037%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20sadly%2C%20due%20to%20the%20