ivation%20of%20heirloom%20seeds%20in%20his%20region.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20conserved%20over%201%2C000%20heirloom%20seed%20varieties%20of%20vegetables%20and%20rice%2C%20and%20trained%20at%20least%2024%2C000%20other%20farmers%20in%20seed%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claims%20his%20company%20%E2%80%98Pabhoi%20Greens%E2%80%99%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20first%20seed%20conservation%20company%20in%20the%20Northeast%E2%80%9D%20where%20farmers%20are%20propagating%20the%20organic%20seeds%20on%20their%20own.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%2C%20these%20farmers%20grow%20heirloom%20seeds%2C%20they%20preserve%20that%20diversity%20and%20ensure%20these%20seeds%20are%20available%20for%20future%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQuest%20of%20a%20farm%20boy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20childhood%2C%20Neelam%20recalls%20being%20compelled%20to%20study%20due%20to%20societal%20pressure.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20a%20farm%20boy!%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20agriculture%20like%20my%20father.%20He%20was%20a%20medical%20doctor%20by%20profession%20but%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20farm%20in%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%20But%20sadly%2C%20Neelam%E2%80%99s%20father%20passed%20away%20from%20a%20stroke%20while%20Neelam%20was%20studying%20in%20Class%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20completing%20Class%2012%2C%20I%20applied%20for%20graduation%20in%20arts%20from%20an%20open%20school.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20so%20disinterested%20that%20I%20neglected%20to%20submit%20assignments%20required%20to%20complete%20the%20degree%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20Pabhoi%20village%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Heirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346322%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHeirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20he%20inherited%2018%20acres%20of%20land%20from%20his%20father.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20read%20Rachel%20Carson%E2%80%99s%20book%20%E2%80%98Silent%20Spring%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20highlighted%20the%20environmental%20harm%20caused%20by%20the%20indiscriminate%20use%20of%20pesticides.%20Motivated%20by%20Carson%E2%80%99s%20message%2C%20Neelam%20resolved%20to%20transition%20his%20land%20into%20an%20organic%20farm.%20By%202003%2C%20he%20had%20successfully%20converted%20his%20entire%20acreage%20to%20organic%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20switching%20to%20organic%20farming%2C%20I%20found%20out%20there%20were%20no%20organic%20seed%20varieties%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20While%20some%20were%20accessible%20for%20rice%2C%20none%20were%20available%20for%20vegetables.%20The%20absence%20of%20reserves%20or%20authenticity%20in%20seed%20sources%20was%20concerning.%20Instead%2C%20the%20market%20was%20saturated%20with%20genetically%20modified%20hybrid%20seeds.%20This%20was%20a%20big%20worrying%20factor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20also%20observed%20that%20most%20of%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20Northeast%20were%20switching%20to%20hybrid%20seeds%20and%20overlooked%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315599%2Fhyderabad-chandana-naveen-gade-seedbasket-agro-services-sell-native-seeds-to-urban-gardeners%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheirloom%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20Green%20Revolution%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20only%20hybrid%20seeds%20were%20to%20be%20supplied%20to%20the%20market%20to%20the%20farmers.%20This%20was%20never%20a%20solution%20for%20an%20%E2%80%98evergreen%E2%80%99%20revolution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20opines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20hybrid%20seeds%20offer%20higher%20yields%20in%20one%20season%2C%20they%20cannot%20be%20saved%20for%20the%20following%20year.%20Consequently%2C%20farmers%20neglected%20heirloom%20seeds%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20their%20sovereignty%20over%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%20Since%20then%2C%20Neelam%E2%80%99s%20mission%20has%20been%20to%20conserve%20decade-old%20seeds%20for%20future%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20the%20traditional%20wisdom%20imparted%20by%20his%20father%20and%20the%20elderly%20in%20the%20village%2C%20he%20set%20out%20in%20search%20of%20these%20heirloom%20treasures.%20In%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20Neelam%20has%20conserved%20nearly%20800%20varieties%20of%20vegetables%20like%20tomatoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20capsicum%2C%20basil%2C%20and%20200%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331636%2Fassam-farmer-starts-rice-library-grows-preserves-indigenous-rice-varieties%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarieties%20of%20ric