0across%20the%20Northeast%20%E2%80%94%20including%20states%20like%20Nagaland%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20them%20grow%20and%20conserve%20their%20own%20heirloom%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20year%2C%20Neelam%20sells%20approximately%208%2C000%20packets%20of%20heirloom%20seeds%20at%20Rs%2099%20each%20to%20farmers.%20With%20these%20seeds%20and%20the%20training%20he%20provides%2C%20farmers%20can%20cultivate%20crops%20and%20harvest%20new%20seeds%20for%20the%20next%20cycle%2C%20ensuring%20sustainable%20food%20security%20%E2%80%94%20a%20goal%20Neelam%20passionately%20pursues%20to%20this%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20Diganata%20Bora%20has%20been%20cultivating%20vegetables%20using%20such%20heirloom%20seeds%20on%20his%20two-acre%20farm%20in%20Paschim%20Manjiri%20village%20of%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20hybrid%20varieties%2C%20we%20get%20good%20yield%20using%20heirloom%20ones.%20In%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5B0.33%20acre%5D%2C%20we%20now%20get%206-7%20quintals%20of%20vegetables%20over%202-2.5%20quintals.%20Additionally%2C%20our%20input%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20zero%20as%20we%20use%20readily%20available%20cow%20dung%20as%20fertiliser.%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20have%20decided%20to%20switch%3B%20now%20our%20soil%20fertility%20has%20also%20improved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Diganata%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20concludes%2C%20%E2%80%9CBack%20when%20I%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F176277%2Fkarnataka-bengaluru-organic-farming-native-seeds-woman%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20were%20no%20resources%20available%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20from.%20Now%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20to%20have%20created%20a%20helpful%20platform%20for%20other%20farmers.%20When%20I%20vis