F295229%2Ftaj-icecream-mumbai-eatery-loved-by-madhubala-makes-natural-icecream-in-wooden-barrels%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20draw%20for%20celebrities%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Ambanis%2C%20the%20Birlas%2C%20and%20the%20Tatas%2C%20they%20must%20be%20doing%20something%20right!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20anyone%20will%20affirm%2C%20a%20menu%20boasting%20scrumptious%20sweets%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20draw%20of%20this%20dairy%20venture%20located%20off%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Princess%20Street.%20It%20is%20its%20century-old%20charm%20and%20the%20recipe%20that%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20generations%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20where%20the%20magic%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20wondering%20why%20the%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20has%20continued%20to%20see%20an%20unwavering%20customer%20base%20for%20over%20108%20years%20now%2C%20the%20proof%20is%20literally%20and%20metaphorically%20in%20the%20pudding.%20The%20history%20of%20the%20business%20ties%20back%20to%20when%20a%20young%20boy%20of%2016%20began%20delivering%20milk%20cans%20to%20homes%20around%20Kalbadevi%20(an%20old%20neighbourhood%20in%20Mumbai).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20Nariman%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20first%20choice%20of%20a%20job.%20Circumstances%20led%20him%20to%20it%2C%20and%20ambition%20paved%20the%20way%20to%20success.%20Since%201916%2C%20when%20Ardeshir%20sold%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327249%2Fkota-engineer-runs-sustainable-dairy-farm-saves-on-electricy-bills-gau-organics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20can%20of%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20seen%20its%20trajectory%20of%20ups%20interspersed%20with%20downs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20fourth%20generation%20settles%20down%20to%20chat%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20they%20say%20challenges%20are%20a%20part%20of%20any%20business.%20What%20set