ought%20multiple%20challenges%20and%20threats%20in%20various%20forms%20in%20his%2014-year%20crusade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20doctor%2C%20we%20see%20families%20starting%20with%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20children.%20We%20become%20a%20part%20of%20these%20units%20as%20they%20remember%20us%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20get%2030%20such%20cases%20every%20month.%20But%20when%20you%20are%20able%20to%20contribute%20towards%20a%20larger%20policy%20change%2C%20you%20are%20able%20to%20impact%20lakhs%20and%20crores%20of%20lives%20known%20and%20unknown%20to%20you.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20whole%20new%20level%20of%20satisfaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Dr%20Nikhil%20Datar)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1705381%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Rajya%2520Sabha%2520has%2520approved%2Con%252017th%2520March%25202020.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajya%20Sabha%20passes%20The%20Medical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202021%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20PIB%20Delhi%20published%20on%207%20March%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711972183000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-2-1711970423.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346145%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Nikhil%20Datar's%20efforts%20led%20to%20the%20amendment%20of%20the%20Medical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20Act%201971%2C%20sparking%20a%20much%20needed%20conversation%20about%20how%20an%20outdated%20and%20medically%20unsound%20law%20was%20harming%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3